# 🎯 Quick GitHub Setup

## Option 1: Automated (Recommended)

```bash
# Run the setup script
./setup-github.sh
```

Then follow the instructions shown.

---

## Option 2: Manual

```bash
# 1. Save current work
git stash

# 2. Switch to main
git checkout main
git checkout -b relationship-adviser
git stash pop

# 3. Add and commit
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: AI-powered Relationship Adviser"

# 4. Create repo on GitHub first, then:
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/relationship-adviser.git

# 5. Push
git push -u origin relationship-adviser
```

---

